Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:08.99,NT,,0,0,0,,远鉴字幕组制作\N{\r原文}  [Visionary] 0day- sub
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:43.74,NT,,0,0,0,,你喜欢那棺材吗\N{\r原文}  Did you like the coffin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:45.45,NT,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢棺材\N{\r原文}  I don't like coffins.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:47.49,NT,,0,0,0,,如您要求\N{\r原文}  Made of the best oak,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:49.20,NT,,0,0,0,,用得是顶级橡木\N{\r原文}  like you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:51.08,NT,,0,0,0,,我看出来了\N{\r原文}  I noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.99,NT,,0,0,0,,我看到他从她房里出来\N{\r原文}  I saw him coming out of her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.24,NT,,0,0,0,,你看到什么了\N{\r原文}  What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:06.83,NT,,0,0,0,,他骑上马就走了 喝得烂醉\N{\r原文}  He mounted his horse and disappeared. He was drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:10.29,NT,,0,0,0,,你怎么确定那就是他 巷子那么黑\N{\r原文}  How could you even be sure it was him? That alley's very dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:11.74,NT,,0,0,0,,他腿瘸了\N{\r原文}  He was limping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:15.16,NT,,0,0,0,,他又不是镇上唯一一个瘸子\N{\r原文}  He's not the only man in town who limps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:16.99,NT,,0,0,0,,据我所知 他是唯一一个左撇子\N{\r原文}  He is the only lefty I know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:18.74,NT,,0,0,0,,他左腿瘸了\N{\r原文}  He was limping on his Ieft leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:20.87,NT,,0,0,0,,你跟别人说过吗\N{\r原文}  Have you told anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:23.12,NT,,0,0,0,,大家都心里有数了 警长\N{\r原文}  Everyone is already thinking it, sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:24.95,NT,,0,0,0,,那你也把嘴闭紧\N{\r原文}  Just keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.45,NT,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\r原文}  Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.79,NT,,0,0,0,,席尔瓦先生来了\N{\r原文}  Mr Silva in person!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.08,NT,,0,0,0,,你怎么样 杰克\N{\r原文}  How are you, jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.45,NT,,0,0,0,,我挺好的\N{\r原文}  I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.33,NT,,0,0,0,,你为什么来镇上\N{\r原文}  What brings you to town?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:57.70,NT,,0,0,0,,背疼得要死 听说镇上有个好医生\N{\r原文}  Oh, my back is killing me and I hear you have a good doctor in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:03:59.45,NT,,0,0,0,,但你气色很好啊\N{\r原文}  But you look well
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:01.74,NT,,0,0,0,,不 是你\N{\r原文}  No, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:03.62,NT,,0,0,0,,看起来气宇轩昂\N{\r原文}  who look impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:05.58,NT,,0,0,0,,换上警长扮相\N{\r原文}  dressed as a Sheriff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.37,NT,,0,0,0,,这不是我的扮相\N{\r原文}  I'm not just dressed as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:08.66,NT,,0,0,0,,我就是警长\N{\r原文}  I am one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:10.16,NT,,0,0,0,,嗯 挺适合你\N{\r原文}  Well, it suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:17.74,NT,,0,0,0,,-我饿了  -嗯\N{\r原文}  -I was hungry. Mm- hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.04,NT,,0,0,0,,你做的\N{\r原文}  You made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:21.74,NT,,0,0,0,,真不知道 你还会做饭\N{\r原文}  I didn't know you could cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:26.16,NT,,0,0,0,,你不了解的事还多呢 席尔瓦\N{\r原文}  There's a great many things you don't know about me, Silva.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.29,NT,,0,0,0,,确实\N{\r原文}  Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.12,NT,,0,0,0,,25年可不短啊\N{\r原文}  25 years is a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.49,NT,,0,0,0,,敬重逢\N{\r原文}  To our reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:35.87,NT,,0,0,0,,敬随你怎么说\N{\r原文}  To whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.58,NT,,0,0,0,,我每次喝酒\N{\r原文}  Every time I drink wine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:43.91,NT,,0,0,0,,都会想起来跟你在墨西哥时\N{\r原文}  I remember when we were in Mexico
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.83,NT,,0,0,0,,和几个妓女一起去地下酒窖\N{\r原文}  and we went down into the cellar with some whores.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.49,NT,,0,0,0,,当时我们真是年少轻狂\N{\r原文}  We were very young and very crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.29,NT,,0,0,0,,一群混混\N{\r原文}  What a bunch of misfits!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:52.91,NT,,0,0,0,,都是各郡渣滓\N{\r原文}  The worst from every county.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:54.62,NT,,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\r原文}  You know
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:56.58,NT,,0,0,0,,我感觉只有我们活了下来\N{\r原文}  I think we're the only ones who've survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:04:58.95,NT,,0,0,0,,为这喝一杯吧\N{\r原文}  Let's drink to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:04.91,NT,,0,0,0,,别这么看我\N{\r原文}  Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.74,NT,,0,0,0,,你想让我怎么看你\N{\r原文}  How do you want me to look at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.66,NT,,0,0,0,,我们疯狂了多久\N{\r原文}  How long did that madness last?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.24,NT,,0,0,0,,两个月\N{\r原文}  Two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.41,NT,,0,0,0,,也不算疯狂\N{\r原文}  And it wasn't madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.54,NT,,0,0,0,,就算喝了酒\N{\r原文}  When I drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.95,NT,,0,0,0,,我也记得那六十天中的每一个瞬间\N{\r原文}  I remember every single one of those sixty days...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:25.29,NT,,0,0,0,,我觉得你喝醉了\N{\r原文}  I think you drink too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:28.37,NT,,0,0,0,,我已经戒了\N{\r原文}  I myself have. given it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.33,NT,,0,0,0,,当然现在我食言了\N{\r原文}  Of course, now I'm contradicting myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.41,NT,,0,0,0,,那就敬食言\N{\r原文}  To your contradictions then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:44.79,NT,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\r原文}  Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.70,NT,,0,0,0,,杰克\N{\r原文}  Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.70,NT,,0,0,0,,我觉得你没对我说真话 席尔瓦\N{\r原文}  Ithink you lied to me, Silva.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.08,NT,,0,0,0,,你是不是想躲在浴缸里\N{\r原文}  Were you hiding in the bathtub?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:27.58,NT,,0,0,0,,我没有在躲\N{\r原文}  Iwasn't hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.87,NT,,0,0,0,,你也该洗个澡了\N{\r原文}  You could use a bath yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:32.66,NT,,0,0,0,,你是在邀请我和你一起洗吗\N{\r原文}  Are you inviting me to take a bath together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:33.95,NT,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\r原文}  No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:37.74,NT,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\r原文}  Don'il
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.91,NT,,0,0,0,,我知道怎么自己擦身子\N{\r原文}  Iknow how to dry myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:43.62,NT,,0,0,0,,快去把衣服穿上\N{\r原文}  You should get dressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:46.45,NT,,0,0,0,,我内裤放哪了\N{\r原文}  Where did I put my underpants?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.37,NT,,0,0,0,,穿我的\N{\r原文}  Take a pair of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:50.41,NT,,0,0,0,,在右边的抽屉里\N{\r原文}  They're in the drawer on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.66,NT,,0,0,0,,你确实撒谎了 席尔瓦\N{\r原文}  And you did lie to mejSilva
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.79,NT,,0,0,0,,你后背完全没事\N{\r原文}  You don't have a bad back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:08.12,NT,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\r原文}  What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.33,NT,,0,0,0,,你也不用看医生\N{\r原文}  And you don't need a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:14.54,NT,,0,0,0,,我就是想跟你喝几杯酒\N{\r原文}  I wanted to have a couple of drinks with you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:16.74,NT,,0,0,0,,趁着还能动\N{\r原文}  while Ican still move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:20.04,NT,,0,0,0,,而且 信不信由你\N{\r原文}  And believe it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:23.33,NT,,0,0,0,,跟马打交道 你的背就会完蛋\N{\r原文}  working with horses destroys your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.95,NT,,0,0,0,,这可说不准\N{\r原文}  No one would ever know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.16,NT,,0,0,0,,我今天早上背不疼了\N{\r原文}  Nothing hurts this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.58,NT,,0,0,0,,你把我完全治好了\N{\r原文}  You cured all my ailments.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.45,NT,,0,0,0,,我有一段时间没觉得这么舒爽了\N{\r原文}  I haven't felt this good in such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:39.70,NT,,0,0,0,,今天打算干什么\N{\r原文}  What are you doing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.20,NT,,0,0,0,,We could go to Hot Mountain river. 我们可以去火山泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:43.83,NT,,0,0,0,,我得上班\N{\r原文}  I've got work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:45.62,NT,,0,0,0,,上班可以等\N{\r原文}  Work can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:51.70,NT,,0,0,0,,不是每天都会有人 穿过沙漠来看你\N{\r原文}  It's not every day someone crosses the desert to come see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:56.66,NT,,0,0,0,,我们已经庆祝过了 我还有事\N{\r原文}  We've celebrated enough. I've got things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:58.08,NT,,0,0,0,,我能帮忙么\N{\r原文}  Can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:08:59.95,NT,,0,0,0,,我可以…\N{\r原文}  Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:02.95,NT,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\r原文}  No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:06.83,NT,,0,0,0,,三天前\N{\r原文}  Three days ago
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:10.41,NT,,0,0,0,,镇上一个女人被杀了\N{\r原文}  a woman was found killed in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:13.33,NT,,0,0,0,,我得找到凶手 让他伏法\N{\r原文}  I've got to find the man who did it and bring him to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:17.16,NT,,0,0,0,,你就不能找个人替你干这活吗 你还是警长呢\N{\r原文}  Can't you find someone else to do it for you? You are the Sheriff
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.74,NT,,0,0,0,,这是荣誉问题\N{\r原文}  It's a question of honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:23.12,NT,,0,0,0,,死的人是我弟妹\N{\r原文}  The woman killed is my brother's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.83,NT,,0,0,0,,我还是镇上的执法人员 记得吧\N{\r原文}  And I'm the law around here, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.70,NT,,0,0,0,,我们的命运可真奇怪\N{\r原文}  Ours is a strange fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.49,NT,,0,0,0,,怎么说\N{\r原文}  What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:35.91,NT,,0,0,0,,你弟妹死了 我们才又在床上相见\N{\r原文}  Your brother's wife had to die for us to find each other in the same bed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:38.33,NT,,0,0,0,,-昨晚  -我们都喝多了\N{\r原文}  ·Last nightLast night we drank too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:40.04,NT,,0,0,0,,喝酒是因为我们很高兴又见到了对方\N{\r原文}  We drank because we were happy to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:43.33,NT,,0,0,0,,那也不能给你儿子脱罪\N{\r原文}  That's not gonna spare your son from paying for what he did!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.49,NT,,0,0,0,,不是他干的\N{\r原文}  He didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:46.74,NT,,0,0,0,,他们是一对 他还虐待她\N{\r原文}  They were lovers, he mistreated her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:49.79,NT,,0,0,0,,他是不是跟你说了 他时不时会来这\N{\r原文}  He must have told you he came here from time to time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:52.20,NT,,0,0,0,,不 我本来想问他关于你的事\N{\r原文}  No, I would've asked him about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.83,NT,,0,0,0,,杰克 别走 我在跟你说话\N{\r原文}  jake, don't walk away, I'm talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:57.62,NT,,0,0,0,,我弟弟死时\N{\r原文}  When my brother died
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.74,NT,,0,0,0,,我跟他保证 会照顾好弟妹\N{\r原文}  I promised him that Iwould look after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.58,NT,,0,0,0,,她不太好哄 但我一直信守承诺\N{\r原文}  She wasn't an easy woman, but I made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:06.08,NT,,0,0,0,,在此之前 我爸爸临死时\N{\r原文}  Before then, on my father's deathbed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.95,NT,,0,0,0,,我保证了要照顾好弟弟\N{\r原文}  I promised him I'd look after my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.79,NT,,0,0,0,,他们两个我谁都不能辜负\N{\r原文}  I can't fail any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:12.49,NT,,0,0,0,,听说你跟她搞起了外遇\N{\r原文}  I heard you had an affair with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:13.58,NT,,0,0,0,,好久以前的事了\N{\r原文}  That was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:14.91,NT,,0,0,0,,当时你弟弟还活着吗\N{\r原文}  Was your brother still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.24,NT,,0,0,0,,不重要\N{\r原文}  It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:21.12,NT,,0,0,0,,重要的是\N{\r原文}  What matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:23.91,NT,,0,0,0,,有人看到一个左腿瘸了的男人\N{\r原文}  is someone saw a man with a limp on his left leg
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.08,NT,,0,0,0,,在她被杀那天晚上离开她家\N{\r原文}  leaving her place the night she was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:29.29,NT,,0,0,0,,你儿子腿要是不瘸 那他什么都不用担心\N{\r原文}  Now, if your son didn't have a limp he'd have nothing to worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:32.70,NT,,0,0,0,,我知道你穿过沙漠来这 是替他来的\N{\r原文}  I understand you've crossed the desert to intervene on his behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:35.45,NT,,0,0,0,,随便那个人都能假装腿瘸陷害他\N{\r原文}  Anyone could have pretended to have a limp to frame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:37.49,NT,,0,0,0,,你为什么来这 席尔瓦\N{\r原文}  Why have you come here, Silva?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.12,NT,,0,0,0,,因为我想见你\N{\r原文}  I came because I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.99,NT,,0,0,0,,我一直就想见你\N{\r原文}  I've been wanting to see you for a long time.
