Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:14.16,NT,,0,0,0,,骑上马 给我滚出这里\N{\r原文}  Now get on the horse and get the fuck out of herel
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.08,0:23:43.58,NT,,0,0,0,,这一枪干净利落 直穿腰部\N{\r原文}  It was a clean shot, straight through the waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.91,0:23:54.70,NT,,0,0,0,,好了 好了…\N{\r原文}  Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.25,0:23:58.62,NT,,0,0,0,,你会没事的\N{\r原文}  You're going to be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:02.33,NT,,0,0,0,,下地狱吧 你这个婊子养的\N{\r原文}  Rot in hell, you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.58,0:24:06.16,NT,,0,0,0,,按住这里\N{\r原文}  Keep pressure on itl
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.58,0:25:32.16,NT,,0,0,0,,你以为你都想好了\N{\r原文}  So you think you got it all figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.37,0:25:35.66,NT,,0,0,0,,这些东西是没办法计算的 杰克\N{\r原文}  These things cannot be calculated, jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.87,0:25:40.54,NT,,0,0,0,,这就是命运 我们谁也躲不过\N{\r原文}  It is destiny and we cannot run away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.87,0:25:43.41,NT,,0,0,0,,什么命运？\N{\r原文}  What destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.75,0:25:44.74,NT,,0,0,0,,我们的\N{\r原文}  Ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.33,0:25:50.70,NT,,0,0,0,,既然你决定跟踪我去找我儿子\N{\r原文}  And since you decided to follow me and look for my son,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.70,0:25:54.20,NT,,0,0,0,,我们三个就注定会相见\N{\r原文}  the three of us were doomed to meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.33,0:25:56.12,NT,,0,0,0,,-我们都带了武器  -胡说八道\N{\r原文}  each of us armed. Bullshitl
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.20,0:25:58.99,NT,,0,0,0,,你开枪打了我 现在又想…绑架我\N{\r原文}  You shot me and now you're...trying to kidnap mel
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.33,0:26:01.45,NT,,0,0,0,,我只想救我儿子\N{\r原文}  I just wanted to save my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.33,0:26:04.95,NT,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 我不得不朝你开枪\N{\r原文}  And I am sorry I had to shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.00,0:26:08.95,NT,,0,0,0,,现在···你以为我尽在你的掌控之中\N{\r原文}  And now... you think you've got me in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.50,0:26:13.12,NT,,0,0,0,,省点力气\N{\r原文}  Don't strain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.54,0:26:14.83,NT,,0,0,0,,别说话了\N{\r原文}  Don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.29,0:26:21.74,NT,,0,0,0,,等我能骑马了 就离开这里\N{\r原文}  As soon as I can ride, I'll leave here
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.79,0:26:24.04,NT,,0,0,0,,我要控告你谋杀未遂\N{\r原文}  and I'll charge you with attempted murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.54,0:26:27.24,NT,,0,0,0,,没人能明白我为什么会射失\N{\r原文}  No one will understand why I missed the shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.41,0:26:29.83,NT,,0,0,0,,更别说我后面还帮你处理伤口了\N{\r原文}  let alone why I treated your wound afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.41,0:26:34.45,NT,,0,0,0,,休息吧\N{\r原文}  Rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.08,0:26:38.95,NT,,0,0,0,,还有的是时间聊\N{\r原文}  There's plenty of time to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.54,0:26:43.95,NT,,0,0,0,,我要是张了嘴\N{\r原文}  The only reason I would open my mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.33,0:26:45.79,NT,,0,0,0,,一定是为了朝你脸上吐口水\N{\r原文}  is to spit in your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.91,0:26:48.41,NT,,0,0,0,,你想怎么恨我都行 杰克\N{\r原文}  You hate me as much as you want, Jake,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.95,0:26:52.70,NT,,0,0,0,,但是你的伤口不会愈合得更快\N{\r原文}  but it won't help your wound to heal any faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.08,0:27:01.29,NT,,0,0,0,,很多年前你问过我···\N{\r原文}  Years ago you asked me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.12,0:27:03.95,NT,,0,0,0,,两个男人在农场上生活\N{\r原文}  what two men could do
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.04,0:27:06.04,NT,,0,0,0,,能干什么\N{\r原文}  living together on a ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.25,0:27:11.16,NT,,0,0,0,,我现在回答你\N{\r原文}  Hl answer you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.58,0:27:15.87,NT,,0,0,0,,他们可以照顾彼此\N{\r原文}  They can look after one another,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.00,0:27:19.74,NT,,0,0,0,,保护彼此\N{\r原文}  protect each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.54,0:27:24.70,NT,,0,0,0,,陪伴彼此\N{\r原文}  they can keep each other company.

